title: Azealia Banks
description:
Here is Azealia Banks' complete discography as at 18-08-2014, with the exception of the Partition Remix with Busta Rhymes and Beyonce.

This one's for all my fellow #KUNTS who are on a limited budget but want to share in the magic that is Azealia Banks. When you're rich and successful be sure to support Azealia Banks by buying her music.

Now before you have a bitch about the organisation, this is just how it works for me. You're more than welcome to organise how you would like. I put in the time to have it suit me, out in the time to have it suit you.

As always, please seed at least what you've downloaded. xo
